			SSH v2, HTTPS and SSH to Serial Ports.<br>
			This profile makes it required to authenticate<br>
			while accessing to Serial Ports.<br><br>
			"Moderate" is the recommended Security Level.<br>
			This profile enables: SSH v1, SSH v2, HTTP, HTTPS,<br>
			Telnet, SSH and Raw connections to Serial Ports,<br>
			ICMP and HTTP redirection to HTTPS.<br>
			Authentication to access Serial Ports is not required.<br><br>
			The use of "Open" profile enables all services: Telnet,<br>
